gecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/11mendy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-qua-nhung-con-so-tieu-bieu-421-191516.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/wc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-qua-nhung-con-so-tieu-bieu-421-191516.html\">World Cup 2018 qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\">World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\