a5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Arsene Wenger sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV&nbsp;c\u1ee7a PSG, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Boreham Wood v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 8-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00f4m 14/7 v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/ars-153114285426350670822.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup 2018 (ICC Cup) v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid (26/7) v\u00e0 PSG (28/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/8 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7: Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal (Hertfordshire, Anh)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7: Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 28/7: Arsenal vs PSG (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8: Arsenal vs Chelsea (Dublin, Ireland)<br>\r\n01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8: Arsenal vs Sevilla (Stockholm, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea-172-191609.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1421","checkdouble":"191606"},{"date":"15:56 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-2019, CLB Man Utd s\u1ebd bay sang B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf International Champions Cup (ICC 2018)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/M_u-660.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU trong h\u00e8 2018 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</h2>\r\n09h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7: Man Utd - Club America<br>\r\n04h00 ng\u00e0y 23/07: Man Utd - SJ Earthquakes<br>\r\n10h05 ng\u00e0y 26/07: AC Milan - Man Utd (ICC 2018)<br>\r\n04h05 ng\u00e0y 29/07: Man Utd - Liverpool (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n07h05 ng\u00e0y 01/08: Man Utd - Real Madrid (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n01h15 ng\u00e0y 6/8: Bayern Munich - Man Utd<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1420","checkdouble":"191607"},{"date":"16:32 19/07","title":"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh HLV West Ham v\u1edbi Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/wilshere-so-sanh-pellegrini-voi-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger. Anh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i West Ham \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere gia nh\u1eadp West Ham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a 2017/18, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi HLV Arsene Wenger n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, Jack Wilshere c\u0169ng n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n. Anh gia nh\u1eadp West Ham theo giao k\u00e8o 3 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Wilshere hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. West Ham \u0111\u00e3 thay David Moyes b\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City, Manuel Pellegrini b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Felipe Anderson hay Andriy Yarmolenko.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/wilshere-so-sanh-pellegrini-voi-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere gia nh\u1eadp West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilshere m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho West Ham. Anh c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Pellegrini s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o gi\u1eefa Wenger v\u00e0 Pellegrini, Wilshere n\u00f3i: \u201cM\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d, Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPellegrini \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Wenger\" title=\"HLV Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/wenger-thua-nhan-sai-lam-khi-o-lai-arsenal-qua-lau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWilshere \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB li\u00ean h\u1ec7 sau khi r\u1eddi Arsenal bao g\u1ed3m Fenerbahce \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ecdn West Ham. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do l\u1edbn t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean, HLV Anh\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n sung s\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho \u0110T Anh. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i CLB, nh\u01b0ng khi West Ham \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean g\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Upton Park v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi CLB.\u201d<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1419","checkdouble":"191608"},{"date":"16:17 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-arsenal.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Arsene Wenger sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV&nbsp;c\u1ee7a PSG, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Boreham Wood v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 8-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00f4m 14/7 v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/ars-153114285426350670822.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup 2018 (ICC Cup) v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid (26/7) v\u00e0 PSG (28/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/8 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7: Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal (Hertfordshire, Anh)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7: Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 28/7: Arsenal vs PSG (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8: Arsenal vs Chelsea (Dublin, Ireland)<br>\r\n01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8: Arsenal vs Sevilla (Stockholm, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea-172-191609.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1418","checkdouble":"191611"},{"date":"16:41 19/07","title":"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i\u201d tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00f4i nh\u1edb xem! \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1998, l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i tr\u00f2n n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng anh Muriel th\u00ec 10 tu\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u1ed5ng c\u00f9ng xem tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1998 gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 d\u00ec. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? B\u00e0 d\u00ec qu\u00fd h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1eeb khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/al.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, cha v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 nh\u1ea3y nh\u00f3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh TV nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111i\u00ean kh\u00f9ng khi Taffarel c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh. Cha t\u00f4i phi m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3. May thay chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh kem tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u cho nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cha t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn mang khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y kem ch\u1ea1y kh\u1eafp nh\u00e0, reo h\u00f2:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i! Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1eaft t\u00f4i l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea5y, \u00f4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0111i\u00ean d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n t\u00f4i sao? B\u1eadn c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u01b0\u01a1i n\u0103m sau, qu\u00fd t\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch, t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00ed &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sao? Kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1ea3 v\u1edd th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n b\u00e1o c\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 ghi:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Alisson Becker: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea3y tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00f9n. D\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng. D\u1ec5 kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Alisson cuu thua xuat than\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/alisson.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u00f4ng anh Muriel. Muriel h\u01a1n t\u00f4i n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u1ed5ng lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i &ldquo;n\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t&rdquo;. Muriel lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdc t\u00f4i ph\u00e1t kh\u00f3c. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng anh trai n\u00e0o tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169ng gi\u1ecfi tr\u00f2 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. Song nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, Muriel gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn n\u00e0o th\u00edch kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8 c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn sau n\u00e0y t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ng\u1ed9 ra, Muriel ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng gene th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n di truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1eb9 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e9m th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh. \u00d4ng c\u1ed1 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u1eaft g\u00f4n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Novo Hamburgo. Cha t\u00f4i gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng anh \u0111\u00e1ng gh\u00e9t n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Ch\u00faa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, anh em t\u00f4i hay xem ra s\u00e2n xem cha t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. T\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i &ldquo;hoang d\u00e3&rdquo; pha ch\u00fat &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh, \u00f4ng lao th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb xung quanh: &ldquo;Cha tao \u0111\u1ea5y! R\u1ed3i tao s\u1ebd b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng hay nh\u01b0 \u1ed5ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i Muriel k\u00e9o t\u00f4i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a \u1ed5ng. Tuy\u1ec7t! G\u00e3 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng to cao&hellip;\u0111\u1ee9a l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t (t\u00f4i) m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;b\u00e9n duy\u00ean&rdquo; v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung g\u1ed7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2002, World Cup t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Anh em t\u00f4i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00ecnh minh, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb socola, b\u00e1nh ng\u00f4, s\u1eefa v\u00e0 m\u1edf TV xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c ng\u1ed9 trong vui s\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Brazil! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 10 tu\u1ed5i, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i khao kh\u00e1t m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n gi\u00e0nh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean con ph\u1ed1 Novo Hamburgo. Khi kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, cha b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0103n nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi. Anh em t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. B\u1ecdn t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng&hellip;c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0m khung th\u00e0nh. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional t\u1ea1i Porto Alegre, m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 x\u1ecbn t\u1ea1i Brazil. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, song, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00f9n!</strong></em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb &ldquo;\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i&rdquo; tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra khi Internacional chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi t\u1eeb Palmeiras. T\u1ec7 th\u1eadt! M\u1ed9t g\u00e3 to x\u00e1c kh\u00e1c sao? T\u00f4i r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5y g\u00e3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy\u1ec7t! Gi\u1edd m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 ba. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u00f4i h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed7i khi b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p \u00f4ng anh cao k\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Muriel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nike Cup &ndash; gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i 14-15. V\u00e0 \u1ed5ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111i ngang k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Muriel, m\u00e1u &ldquo;\u0103n thua&rdquo; l\u1ea1i tr\u1ed7i l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Muriel, em c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u Nike Cup. T\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, suy ngh\u0129 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eeb khung g\u1ed7: Iker Casillas v\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t khi m\u1edbi 17 tu\u1ed5i. Trong khi t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ng\u1ed3i &ldquo;m\u00f2n \u0111\u00edt&rdquo; tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson va anh trai\" title=\"Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/as.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ra th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i kh\u1ecfi Internacinal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u k\u00ec di\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eady th\u00ec, \u00fd t\u00f4i l\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i t\u1eeb 1m70 th\u00e0nh 1m87 ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ed1n. Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u00f4i 16 tu\u1ed5i, khi \u0111ang \u1edf bi\u1ec3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1m b\u1ea1n. Linh t\u00ednh m\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: n\u0103m cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi nh\u1ee1 t\u1eeb \u00f4ng n\u1ed9i. Trong ph\u00fat ch\u1ed1c, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kinh kh\u1ee7ng \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ecdi cho \u00f4ng, t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 ng\u1eebng th\u1edf trong kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u1edd m\u00e1y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>\u00d4ng \u00e0? C\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec v\u1eady \u1ea1?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Nh\u00f3c, ch\u00e1u ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 NGAY B\u00c2Y GI\u1edc!</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Sao \u1ea1? C\u00f3 ai b\u1ecb g\u00ec sao? C\u00f3 ai qua \u0111\u1eddi sao \u00f4ng?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng! Ta b\u00e1o tin ch\u00e1u v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o U17 Brazil th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3n v\u00eda t\u00f4i quay l\u1ea1i sau ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y lo l\u1eafng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c. Tr\u1ea5n t\u0129nh l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee3t nh\u1edb \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u00f9a, t\u00f4i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc xem c\u00f3 n\u00ean v\u1ec1 ngay kh\u00f4ng&hellip;cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u00f4ng ch\u00fa nghi\u00eam t\u00fac g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch 30 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edf website L\u0110B\u0110 Brazil, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1eaft t\u00f4i: &ldquo;Alisson Becker&rdquo;. Ph\u1ea3i! Tuy\u1ec7t c\u00fa m\u00e8o, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n! C\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ee3t tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho, hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh si\u00eau sao sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1n n\u0103m sau, 2013, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Internacional khi 20 tu\u1ed5i. 2015, t\u00f4i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n nhanh \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o n\u00f3. Nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, \u0111ang trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i l\u1ea9m b\u1ea9m &ldquo;Wow! M\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. M\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Brazil. M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i World Cup. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Muriel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson dang la muc tieu hang dau cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/souness-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-trang-thu-mon-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y anh em t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n so s\u00e1nh &ldquo;Li\u1ec7u Alisson c\u00f3 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Muriel kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;. Th\u1eadt l\u00f2ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Muriel, v\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1eeb b\u00e9 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Muriel, anh ta c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n thua c\u1eadu em bao gi\u1edd. Internacional h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi c\u00f3 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp th\u00eam ngo\u00e0i gi\u1edd. Muriel lu\u00f4n k\u00e8 k\u00e8 v\u00e0 qu\u00e1t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00f4i &ldquo;C\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c! T\u1eadp th\u00eam n\u00e0o!&rdquo;. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba, khi th\u1ea5y \u1ed5ng m\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a ngay: &ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0o l\u00e3o gi\u00e0! Nh\u00ecn th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c n\u00e0y m\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u01b0\u01a1ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wow, nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u01a1 b\u00e9 c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. Gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u1ea5t \u0111i t\u00ecnh anh em. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Muriel. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG, t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Brazil, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec \u00f4ng anh Muriel n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel Becker sau khi r\u1eddi Internacional n\u0103m 2017 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 Belenenses, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean th\u1ea3m c\u1ecf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh con ph\u1ed1 h\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Novo Hamburgo, qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a v\u00e0 Muriel t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel \u00e0, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n anh. M\u1ed7i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a em l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a anh. B\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em><strong>L\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch theo:&nbsp;https://www.theplayerstribune.com/en-us/articles/alisson-becker-this-is-for-my-brother<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n</em><strong>H\u1ea2I TH\u01af\u1ee2NG (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1417","checkdouble":"191612"},{"date":"17:19 19/07","title":"Deschamps quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng gh\u1ebf HLV Ph\u00e1p cho Zidane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-deschamps-phat-bieu-ve-dt-phap-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Deschamps ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau 20 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. \u00cdt ai bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch h\u1ee3p d\u1eabn d\u1eaft th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Deschamps b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau khi Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c HLV Real Madrid, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng lung lay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/HLV-Deschamps-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Phap-sau-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Deschamps ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb b\u1ecf c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p (FFF) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Noel Le Graet. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i v\u00ec hai l\u00fd do\u201d. Deschamps n\u00f3i v\u1edbi TF1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy tr\u00ec cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Th\u1ee9 2, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u00ednh tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. T\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i khi c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps phat bieu ve DT Phap sau World Cup 2018\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-deschamps-phat-bieu-ve-dt-phap-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y hay ho. Nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 1-0 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u00ea ph\u00e1n phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Deschamps, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u201cKhi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn\u201d, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 49 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cH\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-phap-tai-world-cup-2018-van-de-chung-toc-chua-the-lam-mo-465-191372.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u1eadu World Cup 2018: V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00f3a m\u1edd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-gianh-cup-vang-thuyet-phuc-chinh-phuc-the-gioi-bang-tinh-than-mayweather-421-191322.html\">Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c: Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n Mayweather</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-thai-tu-mbappe-da-san-sang-ke-vi-421-191299.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u201cTh\u00e1i t\u1eed\u201d Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u1ebf v\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-an-tuong-khong-the-dong-dem-421-191297.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1416","checkdouble":"191613"},{"date":"16:59 19/07","title":"B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Alisson s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec cho Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/ban-hop-dong-66-trieu-bang-alisson-se-dem-lai-nhung-gi-cho-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ederson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap The Kop h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Simon Mignolet l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Klopp tin t\u01b0\u1edfng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Alisson \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua Alisson \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Liverpool-mua-Alisson-Dat-xat-ra-mieng-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Klopp c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra vi\u1ec7c Mignolet ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 c\u1ea3. T\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Anfield v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010 t\u1eeb Sunderland ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, anh m\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Mignolet \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a Klopp th\u00ec Loris Karius l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018. M\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Benzema v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh sau c\u00fa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Bale khi\u1ebfn Liverpool thua 1-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c \u00e9p d\u00e0nh cho Loris Karius l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, NHM Liverpool g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Karius kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai c\u00f2n Mignolet th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet, Liverpool s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Doi-hinh-Liverpool-2018-sieu-khung-o-mua-giai-toi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, t\u1ea1i Anfield c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 bay sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ederson \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 AS Roma, trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1i Olympico t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac cho m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma. Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A (trung b\u00ecnh 0.75 b\u00e0n thua/tr\u1eadn).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" title=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet, theo \u0111\u00f3 trung b\u00ecnh anh c\u1ee9u thua 2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Karius l\u00e0 1.63 c\u00f2n Mignolet ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1.54.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao, theo \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 79.3%. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 Karius (67%) v\u00e0 Mignolet (57%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t r\u1ed9ng ra, Alisson l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ed1t th\u1ee9 3 trong 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 79.3% c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau David De Gea c\u1ee7a MU (80.2%) v\u00e0 Madrid Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid (82.7 %).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 67% c\u00f2n Mignolet ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 58%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Serie A 2017/18 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 79.7%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n (1082) so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ederson (928), anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i t\u1ed1t, Alisson c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u0103ng ra \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Alisson, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Karius. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh sieu khung cua Liverpool o mua giai toi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1415","checkdouble":"191614"},{"date":"17:54 19/07","title":"Sturridge n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/sturridge-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Daniel Sturridge \u1edf Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Roberto Firmino, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/Daniel-Sturridge-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-o-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Sturridge b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb Liverpool \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Sturridge</span> \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Solanke v\u00e0 Danny Ings, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Origi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sturridge ra \u0111i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Everton, Southampton v\u00e0 Wolves l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sturridge l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Sturridge n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/sturridge-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sturridge n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Liverpool, hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9, Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Dortmund. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng HLV s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chester, Tranmere Rovers v\u00e0 Bury ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sturridge \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1414","checkdouble":"191615"},{"date":"09:11 19/07","title":"Man Utd ch\u01b0a g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Diogo Dalot l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00f4 danh n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford t\u1eeb Porto, sau khi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/diogo-dalot-hau-ve-tan-binh-vua-gia-nhap-mu-la-ai-326-187918.html\">Diogo Dalot - h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u00e2n binh v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp M.U l\u00e0 ai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Diogo Dalot ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai th\u00e1ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Diogo Dalot ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai th\u00e1ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Diogo Dalot ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai th\u00e1ng cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a &ldquo;c\u01a1n gi\u00f3 l\u1ea1&rdquo; ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00e0y, s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t ngay trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, Dalot \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng hai th\u00e1ng, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 qua c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi tranh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Diogo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Porto, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n v\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e2u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y m\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u1eabu sao th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i kh\u1ea3 quan v\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ea7m giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Diogo Dalot m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb khi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Porto, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i B d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u1ea3y v\u1ecdt l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Champions League. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111a n\u0103ng, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Antonio Valencia \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\">G\u00f3c M.U: 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Diogo Dalot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi!</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (6/6), th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1: MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1413","checkdouble":"191570"},{"date":"09:12 19/07","title":"Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng \u201cd\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t\u201d Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong \u0111\u1ee3t du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Shaw v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2015/16, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Luke Shaw t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. Sau khi HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00ean thay Louis van Gaal v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean bi \u0111\u00e1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Shaw ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi 17 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Southampton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho Mourinho th\u1eddi gian qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Shaw m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U. &ldquo;5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i th\u1eed s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu&rdquo;, Shaw n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Luke Shaw\" title=\"hau ve Luke Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n cho Mourinho th\u1ea5y trong 4 tu\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn&rdquo;, Shaw n\u00f3i th\u00eam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"Bong da\" type=\"Bong da\">Bongda24h.vn</span>:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-191513.html\">Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-su-ra-di-cua-daley-blind-172-191510.html\">Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Daley Blind?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/me-ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-mu-la-dieu-dang-tiec-172-191474.html\">M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia-172-191421.html\">M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1412","checkdouble":"191573"},{"date":"10:13 19/07","title":"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea5y Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/barca-doi-dembele-lay-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez h\u1ee9a \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Liverpool \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt sau khi ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ghi trung b\u00ecnh 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ m\u00f9a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. V\u00e0 Real bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/real-chi-400-trieu-euro-vao-chuyen-nhuong-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Perez h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e2n l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro Alvaro Odriozola, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 4 ng\u00f4i sao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, Real nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Julen Lopetegui tr\u00e1m ch\u1ed7 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. V\u00e0 sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perez c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0a ra: Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y cho 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Hazard n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real nh\u1eafm Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe song v\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i gia PSG. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, n\u01a1i Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady l\u00e0 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 Raphael Varane. Los Blancos t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Leonardo Bonucci, m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real s\u1ebd g\u00f5 c\u1eeda Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Ronaldo. HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba cho Luka Modric s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-187-191544.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo chia tay Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/theo-hernandez-sap-roi-real-180-191512.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1411","checkdouble":"191575"},{"date":"10:30 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u201cbu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1n\u201d, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd - HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Sarri \u01b0u ti\u00ean &ldquo;d\u1eb9p lo\u1ea1n&rdquo; ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Italia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung chung. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt HLV ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i &ndash; nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB. V\u1ec1 Jorginho, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng, Chelsea \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thay \u0111\u1ed5i 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng xem \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t &ndash; Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c ai ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh &ndash; trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u0169 trang. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Chelsea \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Golovin &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</span><br>\r\nGianfranco Zola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tay ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1410","checkdouble":"191577"},{"date":"09:25 19/07","title":"C\u1eadu b\u00e9 may m\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngh\u0129 g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cau-be-may-man-nhat-viet-nam-nghi-gi-khi-duoc-ho-tong-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng N\u2019Golo Kante, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vinh d\u1ef1 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nThanh S\u01a1n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Luzhniki<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh &ldquo;Ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng danh th\u1ee7&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra World Cup, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n (10 tu\u1ed5i &ndash; TP. HCM) \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 4000 b\u1ea1n nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 \u0111i c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e1m h\u1ed9 l\u00e0 cha c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, 2 cha con Thanh S\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay, chi ph\u00ed \u0103n \u1edf trong 3 ng\u00e0y, 3 \u0111\u00eam t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 4 sao \u1edf Moscow v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi phi\u00ean d\u1ecbch. Em c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC FIFA World Cup h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi &ldquo;h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng&rdquo; N&rsquo;Golo Kante trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft (Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vinh d\u1ef1 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng &ldquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rdquo;, Thanh S\u01a1n cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd em ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd tr\u00ean TV. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eafm tay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng Kante \u1edf chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng Kante \u1edf chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cau-be-may-man-nhat-viet-nam-nghi-gi-khi-duoc-ho-tong-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng N'Golo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, em \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 h\u1ed3i h\u1ed9p, kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft tay th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Mbappe nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh, v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kante d\u1eaft tay ra s\u00e2n, em x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u00ec vui s\u01b0\u1edbng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, N&rsquo;Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Deschamps thay ra t\u1eeb hi\u1ec7p 2. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \" type=\"b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00ea Thanh S\u01a1n, trong th\u1eddi gian 3 ng\u00e0y \u1edf t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Moscow, c\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u0103m th\u00fa r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. 2 cha con Thanh S\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i th\u0103m tu vi\u1ec7n Bogoroditse, \u0111i\u1ec7n Kremlin, nh\u00e0 th\u1edd Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf, Qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ecf, t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 Kotelnicheskaya Naberezhnaya, b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng King Peter v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean &ndash; SV\u0110 Luzhniki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap-421-191507.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap-421-191507.html\">Ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p Macron \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch th\u00fa.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1409","checkdouble":"191578"}]}